title: John Dory Meunière & Nicoise-Style Salad with Pickled Onion & Mustard Vinaigrette
description: Who hasn’t dreamed of escaping to the French Riviera? We hope this dish gets you one step closer - delicate fish kissed with a garlicky, buttery sauce and paired with a vibrant salad of potatoes, green beans and your favourite fresh veg. It’s almost as good as a European holiday.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
